== 理論的模型 ==

[[粒子物理學|粒子物理學]]的[[標準模型|標準模型]]是在理論上描述[[基本粒子|基本粒子]]在四種已知的[[基本相互作用|基本作用力]]中的三種之間，是如何建立起所有的[[物質|物質]]。這種理論能夠預測基本粒子在許多情況下是如何互動的。對超新星，在超新星內的每個微粒，典型的都有1至150[[焦耳|皮焦耳]]（10至數百萬的[[電子伏特|百萬電子伏特]]）的能量。<ref name="izzard">
{{cite journal en| author = R. G. Izzard, E. Ramirez-Ruiz, C. A. Tout
               | title = Formation rates of core-collapse supernovae and gamma-ray bursts
               | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society
               | volume = 348 | issue= 4 | pages = 1215 | date = 2004 }}
</ref> 每個微粒在超新星的環境中所擁有的能量，相對來說是非常小的，因此從粒子物理學的標準模型所做的預測基本上是正確的，但是準模型也許要在高密度上做些修正。<ref name="cc_sims">{{cite conference
                  | author = M. Rampp, R. Buras, H.-Th. Janka, G. Raffelt
                  | title = Core-collapse supernova simulations: Variations of the input physics
                  | booktitle = Proceedings of the 11th Workshop on "Nuclear Astrophysics"
                  | pages = 119–125
                  | date = February 11–16, 2002
                  | location = Ringberg Castle, Tegernsee, Germany
                  | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002nuas.conf..119R
                  | accessdate = 2006-12-14
                  | archive-date = 2017-11-09
                  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171109225657/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002nuas.conf..119R
                  | dead-url = no
                  }}</ref>特別是地球上的[[粒子加速器|粒子加速器]]已經可以創造出比在超新星內發現的能量更高的高能粒子。<ref>{{cite journal en
               | author=The OPAL Collaboration, K. Ackerstaff ''et al.''
               | title=Tests of the Standard Model and Constraints on New Physics from Measurements of Fermion-pair Production at 189 GeV at LEP.
               | journal=[Submitted to] The European Physical Journal C
               | year=1998
               | volume=2
               | pages=441–472
               | url=http://publish.edpsciences.com/articles/epjc/abs/1998/05/epjc851/epjc851.html
               | accessdate=2007-03-18
               | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070321053655/http://publish.edpsciences.com/articles/epjc/abs/1998/05/epjc851/epjc851.html
               | archive-date=2007-03-21
               | dead-url=yes
               }}</ref>但是，這些實驗只是單獨的粒子對粒子之間的交互作用，而在高密度的超新星內部很可能會導致新的作用。在超新星內，微中子可能和其它的粒子之間有[[弱核力|弱核力]]，這一部分應該要好好的了解。無論如何，質子和微中子之間的[[強核力|強核力]]，仍是所知甚少的部分。<ref>{{cite web en 
 |author=Staff 
 |date=2004-10-05 
 |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2004/public.html 
 |title=The Nobel Prize in Physics 2004 
 |publisher=Nobel Foundation 
 |accessdate=2007-05-30 
 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503191526/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/physics/laureates/2004/public.html 
 |archivedate=2007-05-03 
 |deadurl=yes 
 }}</ref>

對Ⅱ型超新星尚不瞭解的主要問題是，微中子的噴發如何將能量轉移給恆星其餘的部分，產生造成恆星爆炸的衝激波。從以上的研究，僅需要轉移1%的能量就可以導致爆炸，但即使參與的微粒之間的交互作用已經被充分的了解，要解釋如何調動這1%的能量仍是非常困難的。 在1990年代，一種複雜的[[對流反轉|對流反轉]]模型被提出來，它建議經由對流作用，無論是由底層的微中子往上，或是上層的一般物質往下，完整的過程先毀壞原來的恆星，比鐵重的元素在爆炸中經由電子捕獲而形成，並且在微中子的壓力逼迫下形成"微中子層"的邊界，種入在四周圍充滿了恆星早先形成的氣體和塵埃雲氣的空間之中。<ref name="pop-sci-dec-2006">{{cite journal en| last=Stover | first=Dawn | title=Life In A Bubble | journal=Popular Science | volume=269 | issue=6 | year=2006 | pages=16}}</ref>

由標準模形塑造的微中子物理學，是理解這個過程的關鍵。<ref name="cc_sims" />其他關鍵領域的研究還包括造成恆星死亡的等離子體[[流體動力學|流體動力學]]：當核心塌縮時它的行為如何，何時和如何確定「衝激波」的形成，何時和如何「停頓」，又如何再活化。<ref>{{cite journal en | author=H.-Th. Janka, K. Langanke, A. Marek, G. Martinez-Pinedo, B. Mueller | title=Theory of Core-Collapse Supernovae | journal=Bethe Centennial Volume of Physics Reports [submitted] | year=2006 | url=http://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0612072 | accessdate=2007-02-01 | archive-date=2015-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223003453/http://arxiv.org/abs/astro-ph/0612072 | dead-url=no }}</ref>[[電腦模擬|電腦模擬]]曾經很成功的計算出Ⅱ型超新星在衝激波形成之後的行為。在不理會爆炸的第一秒鐘，並且假設爆炸已經開始，[[天文物理學家|天文物理學家]]已經能夠詳細的預測超新星產生的元素和預期超新星的[[光度曲線|光度曲線]]。<ref>{{cite journal en | author=S.I. Blinnikov, F.K. Röpke, E.I. Sorokina, M. Gieseler, M. Reinecke, C. Travaglio, W. Hillebrandt, M. Stritzinger | title=Theoretical light curves for deflagration models of type Ia supernova | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics | year=2006 | volume=453 | issue=1 | pages=229–240 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2006astro.ph..3036B | accessdate=2007-02-01 | archive-date=2018-10-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005094544/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2006astro.ph..3036B | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>
{{cite journal en| last=Young | first=Timothy R. | title=A Parameter Study of Type II Supernova Light Curves Using 6 M He Cores | journal=The Astrophysical Journal | year=2004 | volume=617 | issue=1 | pages=1233–1250 | url=http://www.journals.uchicago.edu/cgi-bin/resolve?id=doi:10.1086/425675 | accessdate = 2007-02-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite conference | author = A. Heger, T. Rauscher, R.D. Hoffman, S.E. Woosley | title = Nucleosynthesis in Massive Stars Using Extended Adaptive Nuclear Reaction Networks | booktitle = AIP Conference Proceedings | volume = 561 | pages = 44 | publisher = American Institute of Physics | date = September 4–7, 2000 | location = Tours, France | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2001tsnp.symp...44H | accessdate = 2006-12-13 | id = ISBN 1-56396-996-3 | archive-date = 2017-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171114223041/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2001tsnp.symp...44H | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 光度曲線和不尋常的光譜 ==

[[File:SNIIcurva.png|right]]
當Ⅱ型超新星的[[光譜|光譜]]被研究之後，一般說來會有氫原子吸收能量特徵的[[巴耳末系|巴耳末吸收線]] —，這條譜線的出現可以用來與[[Ia超新星|Ia超新星]]有所區別。

當Ⅱ型超新星的光度被描繪一段時間之後，會在典型特徵的亮度高峰之後出現光度的下降，光度區線平均以每天0.008[[絕對星等|星等]]的斜率下降，這比Ia超新星的速率要慢許多。II型超新星可以依據光度曲線的形式分成兩種類型，Ⅱ-L超新星在亮度高峰之後呈現穩定的（[[線性|線性]]）光度下降。相對的，Ⅱ-P超新星的光度曲線在下降中會有獨具特色的平坦展開（稱為高原），在這期間光度以更平緩的速率下降。Ⅱ-L的淨光度衰減率是低於每天0.012星等，相較於Ⅱ-P的淨衰減率是每天0.0075星等。
<ref name="comparative_study">{{cite journal en | author=J. B. Doggett, D. Branch | title=A Comparative Study of Supernova Light Curves | journal=Astronomical Journal | year=1985 | volume=90 | pages=2303–2311 | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1985AJ.....90.2303D | accessdate=2007-02-01 | archive-date=2019-10-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017185323/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1985AJ.....90.2303D | dead-url=no }}</ref>

因此造成了兩這者的光度曲線有所不同，在Ⅱ-L超新星的狀況下，原始恆星的氫殼機乎完全都被清除了<ref name="comparative_study" />。Ⅱ-P超新星的高原是外面[[不透明|不透明]]層的變化造成的，衝激波剝離了氫原子的電子，將外面的氫[[電離|游離]]，造成了不透明度重大的改變，阻止了部分爆炸時產生的光子脫離。一旦這些氫開始冷卻並再結合成原子，外層就逐漸變得透明。<ref>{{cite web en | url = http://cosmos.swin.edu.au/lookup.html?e=typeiisupernovalightcurves | title = Type II Supernova Light Curves | publisher = Swinburne University of Technology | accessdate = 2007-03-17 | archive-date = 2019-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191017110755/http://astronomy.swin.edu.au/cosmos/T/Type+II+Supernova+Light+Curves | dead-url = no }}</ref>

Ⅱ型超新星的光譜會有不尋常的形狀，Ⅱn超新星可能有噴出物與星周物質產生交互作用，<ref>{{cite journal en
               | author=A. Pastorello, M. Turatto, S. Benetti, E. Cappellaro, I.J. Danziger, P.A. Mazzali, F. Patat, A.V. Filippenko, D.J. Schlegel, T. Matheson
               | title=The type IIn supernova 1995G: interaction with the circumstellar medium
               | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society
               | year=2002
               | volume=333
               | issue=1
               | pages=27–38
               | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002MNRAS.333...27P
               | accessdate=2007-02-01
               | archive-date=2007-10-11
               | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011134732/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2002MNRAS.333...27P
               | dead-url=no
               }}</ref> Ⅱb超新星可能是更重的恆星因為伴星的[[潮汐力|潮汐剝離]]失去了大部分但不是全部的氫殼。當IIb的噴出物膨脹時，氫殼很快的變得更為[[光學厚度|透明]]，而顯露出更深的內層。<ref>{{cite journal en
               | last=Utrobin
               | first=V. P.
               | title=Nonthermal ionization and excitation in Type IIb supernova 1993J
               | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics
               | year=1996
               | volume=306
               | pages=219–231
               | url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996A&A...306..219U
               | accessdate=2007-02-01
               | archive-date=2007-10-11
               | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011134637/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1996A%26A...306..219U
               | dead-url=no
               }}</ref>

== Ⅱn型超新星==
"n"代表狹窄，這表示出現在光譜中的氫譜線寬度是非常狹窄或是適中的。在寬度適中的事例中，來自爆炸的噴出物可能與星體附近的氣體 － 星周環的介質 － 有著強烈的互動<ref>{{cite journal|title=Optical spectra of supernovae|date=1997-09-01|doi=10.1146/annurev.astro.35.1.309|journal=Annual Review of Astronomy and Astrophysics|pages=309–355|volume=35|issue=1|issn=0066-4146|url=http://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.astro.35.1.309|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Alexei V. Filippenko|archive-date=2019-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190216154525/https://www.annualreviews.org/doi/10.1146/annurev.astro.35.1.309|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
 | first=A. | last=Pastorello
 | coauthors=Turatto, M.; Benetti, S.; Cappellaro, E.; Danziger, I. J.; Mazzali, P. A.; Patat, F.; Filippenko, A. V.; Schlegel, D. J.; Matheson, T.
 | title=The type IIn supernova 1995G: interaction with the circumstellar medium
 | journal=Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society
 | year=2002 | volume=333 | issue=1 | pages=27–38
 | bibcode=2002MNRAS.333...27P
 | doi=10.1046/j.1365-8711.2002.05366.x |arxiv = astro-ph/0201483 }}</ref>。有徵兆指出它們與在爆炸前損失大量質量的[[高光度藍變星|高光度藍變星]]類似，有著相同的起源<ref>{{cite arxiv |eprint=1010.2689 |author1=Michael Kiewe |author2=Avishay Gal-Yam |author3=Iair Arcavi |author4=Leonard |author5=Emilio Enriquez |author6=Bradley Cenko |author7=Fox |author8=Dae-Sik Moon |author9=Sand |title=Caltech Core-Collapse Project (CCCP) observations of type IIn supernovae: typical properties and implications for their progenitor stars |class=astro-ph.CO |year=2010}}</ref>。[[SN_2005gl|SN 2005gl]]是IIn型超新星的一個例子；[[SN_2006gy|SN 2006gy]]，一顆極端高能超新星，也許是另一個例子<ref>{{cite journal|title=Spectral Evolution of the Extraordinary Type IIn Supernova 2006gy|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|volume=709|issue=2|pages=856|url=http://stacks.iop.org/0004-637X/709/i=2/a=856|date=2010|doi=10.1088/0004-637x/709/2/856|issn=0004-637X|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Nathan Smith, Ryan Chornock, Jeffrey M. Silverman, Alexei V. Filippenko, Ryan J. Foley}}</ref>。

==Ⅱb型超新星 ==
Ⅱb型超新星的光譜最初有一條微弱的氫線，這也是它被分為Ⅱ型超新星的緣故。在它的光度曲線中，於第一個高峰之後有第二個高峰，這非常類似於[[Ib和Ic超新星|Ib超新星]]。其母恆星可能是聯星系中的一顆巨星，在與伴星的交互作用中失去了絕大部分的氫，只留下了幾乎全部是氦的核心<ref name=Utrobin>{{cite journal | doi= | last=Utrobin | first=V. P. | title=Nonthermal ionization and excitation in Type IIb supernova 1993J | journal=Astronomy and Astrophysics | year=1996 | volume=306 | issue=5940 | pages=219–231 | bibcode=1996A&A...306..219U }}</ref>。當Ⅱb超新星爆炸時，它的噴出物使氫氣層很快的變成[[光深度|更為透明]]並且露出更深的內層<ref name=Utrobin/>。Ⅱb超新星，這一類型的經典例子是[[SN_1993J|SN 1993J]]<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.nature.com/doifinder/10.1038/364507a0|pages=507–509|title=A type IIb model for supernova 1993J|journal=Nature|volume=364|issue=6437|issn=1476-4687|date=1993/08|language=En|accessdate=2018-04-02|doi=10.1038/364507a0|author=K. Nomoto, T. Suzuki, T. Shigeyama, S. Kumagai, H. Yamaoka, H. Saio|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017110751/https://www.nature.com/articles/364507a0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=Type IIb Supernovae with Compact and Extended Progenitors|journal=The Astrophysical Journal Letters|volume=711|issue=1|pages=L40|url=http://stacks.iop.org/2041-8205/711/i=1/a=L40|date=2010|doi=10.1088/2041-8205/711/1/l40|issn=2041-8205|language=en|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Roger A. Chevalier, Alicia M. Soderberg}}</ref>，另一個例子是[[仙后座A|仙后座A]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=The Cassiopeia A Supernova Was of Type IIb|journal=Science|date=2008-05-30|doi=10.1126/science.1155788|url=http://science.sciencemag.org/content/320/5880/1195|language=en|volume=320|issue=5880|pages=1195–1197|issn=0036-8075|accessdate=2018-04-02|author=Oliver Krause, Stephan M. Birkmann, Tomonori Usuda, Takashi Hattori, Miwa Goto, George H. Rieke, Karl A. Misselt|archive-date=2018-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180601203718/http://science.sciencemag.org/content/320/5880/1195|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

